    <id>https://community.sap.com/t5/technology-q-a/program-variant-parameter-with-value-despite-quot-save-field-without-value/qaq-p/13937389</id>
    <title>Program variant parameter with value despite "save field without value"</title>
    <updated>2024-11-13T22:00:46.965000+01:00</updated>
    <author>
      <name>Sandra_Rossi</name>
      <uri>https://community.sap.com/t5/user/viewprofilepage/user-id/145194</uri>
    </author>
    <content>&lt;P&gt;I'm a little surprised by a bug in my ECC 6 EHP 7 system. I see a few old program variants of a custom program, with a parameter P_FILE_1 which has both one non-empty value and the checkbox "save field without value" checked.&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;If I save the program variant, the value is emptied, as I expect (back to the normal situation).&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;The program RSVARDOC_610 doesn't fix the issue (note that RSVARDOC_NEW doesn't exist in my system). RSVCHECK says that the program variant is fine.&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;For information, running the program with such a weird program variant (having&amp;nbsp;both a non-empty value and the checkbox "save field without value" checked), behaves like if the checkbox was not checked, i.e. the parameter field in the selection screen is changed with the value from the program variant.&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;&lt;span class="lia-inline-image-display-wrapper lia-image-align-inline" image-alt="Sandra_Rossi_0-1731530842850.png" style="width: 400px;"&gt;&lt;img src="https://community.sap.com/t5/image/serverpage/image-id/190622i30CA593CE65D85B6/image-size/medium?v=v2&amp;amp;px=400" role="button" title="Sandra_Rossi_0-1731530842850.png" alt="Sandra_Rossi_0-1731530842850.png" /&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;&lt;span class="lia-inline-image-display-wrapper lia-image-align-inline" image-alt="Sandra_Rossi_1-1731530895962.png" style="width: 400px;"&gt;&lt;img src="https://community.sap.com/t5/image/serverpage/image-id/190624i520B2F11A9116B80/image-size/medium?v=v2&amp;amp;px=400" role="button" title="Sandra_Rossi_1-1731530895962.png" alt="Sandra_Rossi_1-1731530895962.png" /&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;NB: only one selection screen.&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;Did you hear about this "bug"? I didn't find any SAP note about it.&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;Thanks.&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;Sandra&lt;/P&gt;</content>
    <link href="https://community.sap.com/t5/technology-q-a/program-variant-parameter-with-value-despite-quot-save-field-without-value/qaq-p/13937389"/>
    <published>2024-11-13T22:00:46.965000+01:00</published>
  </entry>
