    <content>&lt;P&gt;Hey folks,&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;We are trying to solve an issue during the creation of a Purchase Order (PO).&lt;BR /&gt;As per the standard, when we add materials to the line items, the system provides traffic light indicators.&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;The only available BAdI (ME_PROCESS_PO_CUST) does not stop the program when attempting to check these indicators.&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;The goal is that if the traffic lights are "red," meaning error messages, the program should NOT save the document.&lt;BR /&gt;&lt;BR /&gt;i'll show below step by step.&lt;BR /&gt;1) We add one material&amp;nbsp;&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;&lt;span class="lia-inline-image-display-wrapper lia-image-align-inline" image-alt="Jah3zzi_0-1731665743790.png" style="width: 400px;"&gt;&lt;img src="https://community.sap.com/t5/image/serverpage/image-id/191254i449B3B88E6396A87/image-size/medium?v=v2&amp;amp;px=400" role="button" title="Jah3zzi_0-1731665743790.png" alt="Jah3zzi_0-1731665743790.png" /&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;2) press "Save"&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;&lt;span class="lia-inline-image-display-wrapper lia-image-align-inline" image-alt="Jah3zzi_1-1731665817371.png" style="width: 400px;"&gt;&lt;img src="https://community.sap.com/t5/image/serverpage/image-id/191255iD2E53FDA91A385D8/image-size/medium?v=v2&amp;amp;px=400" role="button" title="Jah3zzi_1-1731665817371.png" alt="Jah3zzi_1-1731665817371.png" /&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;3) then my BADI ME_PROCESS_PO_CUST is activated.&lt;BR /&gt;and it's shows the message that it should stop the TCode of PO.&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;&lt;span class="lia-inline-image-display-wrapper lia-image-align-inline" image-alt="Jah3zzi_2-1731665944786.png" style="width: 400px;"&gt;&lt;img src="https://community.sap.com/t5/image/serverpage/image-id/191256iC792040BB38522F0/image-size/medium?v=v2&amp;amp;px=400" role="button" title="Jah3zzi_2-1731665944786.png" alt="Jah3zzi_2-1731665944786.png" /&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;4) Pressing "F8" an it's appear the pop-up that we can chose if we can proceed further with the PO.&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;&lt;span class="lia-inline-image-display-wrapper lia-image-align-inline" image-alt="Jah3zzi_3-1731666065087.png" style="width: 400px;"&gt;&lt;img src="https://community.sap.com/t5/image/serverpage/image-id/191258i30F8C58485E035E0/image-size/medium?v=v2&amp;amp;px=400" role="button" title="Jah3zzi_3-1731666065087.png" alt="Jah3zzi_3-1731666065087.png" /&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;5) the issue is that we should not proceed with the "hold" button because we have the red-lights "red", but my check on step 3 is not stopping the Parking of the PO.&lt;BR /&gt;&lt;BR /&gt;you folks have any ideas how to break the creation of the PO?&lt;BR /&gt;&lt;BR /&gt;thanks in advance for your collab,&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;G. &amp;amp; E.&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;&lt;BR /&gt;&lt;BR /&gt;&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;&lt;BR /&gt;&lt;BR /&gt;&lt;/P&gt;</content>
